sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673502b7da575b4c6971e781aaff41826f9d7378","tid":273165,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱流失速率關人體同環境溫差事<br />\n溫差高 熱流失得快所以你覺得凍<br />\n溫差低 啲熱焗住走唔到 所以你覺得熱<br />\n冇溫差 熱幾乎冇淨流失 應該超熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲有一個問題就係<br />\n我知道人一日有好一部分能量用於維持身體溫度<br />\n巴打你都提及到降溫係透過熱流失<br />\n但其實可唔可以令人減少用於維持溫度嘅能量消耗 咁又可以冇咁熱 又可以減少能量消耗"},{"pid":"83561347175cb0b2ea3c95be1279ab5de80ba515","tid":273165,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://health.udn.com/health/story/10561/1838741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhealth.udn.com%2Fhealth%2Fstory%2F10561%2F1838741&d=nsKiQur%2FxJnSfmrrLqXCDxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=a0c0674e\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.udn.com/health/story/10561/1838741</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shs.edu.tw/works/essay/2008/01/2008012223423815.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shs.edu.tw%2Fworks%2Fessay%2F2008%2F01%2F2008012223423815.pdf&d=nsKiQur%2FxJnSfmrrLqXCDxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=cc6fad0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.shs.edu.tw/works/essay/2008/01/2008012223423815.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"f5c7d4432915aeb80f4511f476c7647a297dc1ef","tid":273165,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"香港嗰種濕熱係難頂啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f649ffdc02cd74358cb01c786fdae80e4d93e4","tid":273165,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9292fc1228bac6d7efb979484562d7596823e952","tid":273165,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://health.udn.com/health/story/10561/1838741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhealth.udn.com%2Fhealth%2Fstory%2F10561%2F1838741&d=nsKiQur%2FxJnSfmrrLqXCDxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=a0c0674e\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.udn.com/health/story/10561/1838741</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shs.edu.tw/works/essay/2008/01/2008012223423815.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shs.edu.tw%2Fworks%2Fessay%2F2008%2F01%2F2008012223423815.pdf&d=nsKiQur%2FxJnSfmrrLqXCDxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=cc6fad0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.shs.edu.tw/works/essay/2008/01/2008012223423815.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7559ea3410a5efb9b5425395a51e2d9b70e6467d","tid":273165,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熱流失速率關人體同環境溫差事<br />\n溫差高 熱流失得快所以你覺得凍<br />\n溫差低 啲熱焗住走唔到 所以你覺得熱<br />\n冇溫差 熱幾乎冇淨流失 應該超熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲有一個問題就係<br />\n我知道人一日有好一部分能量用於維持身體溫度<br />\n巴打你都提及到降溫係透過熱流失<br />\n但其實可唔可以令人減少用於維持溫度嘅能量消耗 咁又可以冇咁熱 又可以減少能量消耗</blockquote><br />\n人體嘅體溫有兩大來源<br />\n一部分係你咁講靠燒能量<br />\n另一部分係來自本身體內嘅chemical reaction <br />\n所以唔係想降就降<br />\n<br />\n同埋人體嘅溫度唔可以話降就降<br />\n因為跌幾度係講緊有啲好重要嘅reaction會行唔到<br />\n係會死人<br />\n<br />\n就算係會冬眠嘅動物<br />\n好似啲熊咁<br />\n佢地都會keep住個體溫<br />\n但減慢晒其他metabolism"},{"pid":"fb0ad7ec3c3b250d582051ba937e7f1fe98e5dc0","tid":273165,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:33:21.000Z","msg":"睇晒都唔明<br />\n<br />\n咩係體感温度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4c49dd24b0fd6a11581b2052c68da33af82cca","tid":273165,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:17:04.000Z","msg":"濕度令人散不到熱"},{"pid":"a74d812d3b67fef2b7206a70bd5eda41017cb232","tid":273165,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:22:21.000Z","msg":"氣溫上升<br />\n身體散熱慢"}]}